20 rate of one and six tenths of a cent ($0.016) for each milliliter or milligram of
21 tetrahydrocannabinol contained in a cannabis-infused beverage for human
22 consumption sold, used, or distributed by sale or gift in the Commonwealth of
23 Kentucky on every:
24 (a) Wholesaler;
25 (b) Distributor;
26 (c) Manufacturer permitted by the Department for Public Health; and
27 (d) Direct shipper.
