1 6. Hexahydrocannabinol (HHC) (CAS # 36403-90-4 for 9(R)-HHC and
2 36403-91-5 for 9(S)-HHC);
3 7. Delta-8-iso-tetrahydrocannabinol (delta-8-iso-THC) (CAS # 23050-47-
4 7);
5 8. Delta-4,8-iso-tetrahydrocannabinol (delta 4(8)-iso-THC) (CAS #
6 23050-59-1);
7 9. 9(R) Hexahydrocannabinol (9(R)-HHC) (CAS # 23050-47-7); and
8 10. 9(S) Hexahydrocannabinol (9(S)-HHC) (CAS # 36403-91-5).
9 (c) The proficiency test samples shall be of known concentration, preparation
