23 sale of which are required to be included in the measure of the sales tax, and every
24 person engaged in making sales for resale;
25 (45) (a) "Storage" includes any keeping or retention in this state for any purpose
26 except sale in the regular course of business or subsequent use solely outside
27 this state of tangible personal property, digital property, or prewritten
