22 is described in or classified pursuant to KRS Chapter 218A in the two (2)
23 years immediately preceding the application;
24 (c) Has been convicted of any misdemeanor directly or indirectly attributable to
25 the use of alcoholic beverages or cannabis-infused beverages in the two (2)
26 years immediately preceding the application;
27 (d) Is under the age of twenty-one (21) years; or
