18 entity in which they were directly or indirectly interested, has had any license
19 revoked for cause or has been convicted of a violation of any statute within
20 KRS Chapters 241 to 244, until the expiration of the later of two (2) years
21 from the date of the revocation or two (2) years from the date of conviction.
